metadata.name: I
metadata.description:
In recent years, the use of artificial intelligence in art has grown exponentially, creating unique and thought-provoking pieces. 

In Synthetica, I used AI algorithms to create surreal and otherworldly cityscapes and enhance my original photographs, creating a fusion of the digital and the organic. 

The use of AI allows me to explore new creative possibilities and push the boundaries of traditional photography. Each image in the series is a unique and stunning exploration of the intersection between technology and art.

The use of AI in Syntheca also raises interesting questions about the role of technology in art and the blurring of the lines between the natural and the artificial.
